{"tid":1566131,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Web][207]尼奧寵物Neopets! 尼臭月圓\f","createTime":"2019-09-13T12:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T01:22:11.000Z","uid":21203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ccab6d96446870eebf9148765ca5a1303c0428f7","tid":1566131,"uid":21203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:22:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">流行歐美、最風行的虛擬寵物遊戲！除了養寵物，還有許多小遊戲可以玩哦！<br />\n現在就加入尼奧世界吧！簡單、快捷，而且完全免費<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[url]<a href=\"http://www.neopets.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neopets.com&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=2c7b73cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.neopets.com</a>[/url]</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc11/bananaaming/haha-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi213.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fcc11%2Fbananaaming%2Fhaha-3.jpg&h=610ea8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ZWHSWw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0ZWHSWw.png&h=b9743021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以尼奧寵物為主軸，延伸發展出尼奧世界</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尼奧寵物五大目標:<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">賺錢、養靚寵、收藏物品、練寵戰鬥、參與劇情活動</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&darr;新手必看,老手必讀&darr;</span></span></strong></div><br />\n入左尼奧 養左第一隻寵 大家唔知道可以做咩 ? 等巴打私人教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講左養寵先<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.neopets.com/calendar.phtml \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neopets.com%2Fcalendar.phtml%20&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=83972470\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.neopets.com/calendar.phtml </a><br />\n&uarr;呢個係尼奧世界日曆 多數「限量版寵物」可以係佢地既寵物日到養到<br />\n「限量版寵物」詳情:<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=specialpets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Dspecialpets&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=095dc2a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=specialpets</a><br />\n其他養寵方法有:孤兒院領養或同人交換<br />\n尼奧二大特別寵(不能於寵物日領養):<br />\n<img src=\"http://pets.neopets.com/cp/bg85wvqh/1/4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpets.neopets.com%2Fcp%2Fbg85wvqh%2F1%2F4.png&h=f39391b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://pets.neopets.com/cp/3jbj64kr/1/4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpets.neopets.com%2Fcp%2F3jbj64kr%2F1%2F4.png&h=0cb8d307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左)特雷<br />\n由特雷蛋孵出 一粒海盜特雷蛋 約值200k~300k(20萬~30萬)<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/mfo_draikegg_pirate.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fmfo_draikegg_pirate.gif&h=e0b205c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右)狂妄龍<br />\n以前主要由狂妄龍寵物玩伴變出<br />\n現在多數人買魔力海盜狂妄龍絨毛玩具 約值200k~300(20萬~30萬)<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/plu_krawk_magical_pirate.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fplu_krawk_magical_pirate.gif&h=db38da1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n使用蛻變藥水的話價錢相若<br />\n開Post專用:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XHnmsB1Ky3i-RZRZy84zCrxd78CXfDJoumiGuYZawgY/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1XHnmsB1Ky3i-RZRZy84zCrxd78CXfDJoumiGuYZawgY%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=3efd2964\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XHnmsB1Ky3i-RZRZy84zCrxd78CXfDJoumiGuYZawgY/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"1edae6f8855ba346aca3079600a5c9edd8e8329d","tid":1566131,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:22:23.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link t