/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Faltador%2Fmisc%2Fneopoints_bag_07b7353930.gif&h=826116c9&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">儲錢篇</span></span><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/altador/misc/neopoints_bag_07b7353930.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Faltador%2Fmisc%2Fneopoints_bag_07b7353930.gif&h=826116c9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>每日必按</strong></span> </span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=dailies\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Ddailies&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=bb32705b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=dailies</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 顧名思義,同我每日入去曬啲Link佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">搶貨攻略</span><br />\n自認眼光獨到,網速夠快?<br />\n新手搶貨攻略:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=restocking\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Drestocking&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=2b0f1dd6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=restocking</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">股票教學</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=neopian_stock_market\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Dneopian_stock_market&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=6125e8cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=neopian_stock_market</a><br />\n太長唔想睇? 巴打我用一句整理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;<strong><ins>只買每股<span style=\"color: green;\">15np</span>的股票,買<span style=\"color: green;\">1000</span>股,到你死果日就會升值架喇</ins></strong>&quot;</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">職業介紹所</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.neopets.com/faerieland/employ/employment.phtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neopets.com%2Ffaerieland%2Femploy%2Femployment.phtml&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=8ea84f3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.neopets.com/faerieland/employ/employment.phtml</a><br />\n上面係精靈仙境職業介紹所Link,下面係攻略Link<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=employment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Demployment&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=2f2fccea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=employment</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">玩遊戲</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=50k_a_day\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3D50k_a_day&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=fc1bfe5d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=50k_a_day</a><br />\n新手玩遊戲係最快的賺錢法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">拍賣行</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=auctions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Dauctions&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=472b254e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=auctions</a><br />\n成日有傻仔低價賣貴野,但你bid唔bid到係另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599eca7239a7525f794fef77cc0d89480d4165da","tid":1566131,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c758134787e1bc2dd32ef1ad203aa39178ad9c2f","tid":1566131,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:24:23.000Z","msg":"個ac玩13年被凍<br />\n原因係username<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414207b674ddaa335d26c20aec435ca3eccccfa6","tid":1566131,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:24:29.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"862c22c029d9fbbadad062faa017dbac0ba264dd","tid":1566131,"uid":21203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/maractitepaintbrush.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fmaractitepaintbrush.gif&h=bdf69821&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/paintbrush_water.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpaintbrush_water.gif&h=75999fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">上色篇</span></span></strong><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/paintbrush_water.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpaintbrush_water.gif&h=75999fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/maractitepaintbrush.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fmaractitepaintbrush.gif&h=bdf69821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解人地隻寵顏色咁靚,我就得紅黃藍綠</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/paintbrush_pastel.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpaintbrush_pastel.gif&h=13632e18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/pot_kacheek_baby.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpot_kacheek_baby.gif&h=6e73adaa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/pot_kyrii_rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpot_kyrii_rg.gif&h=2ff39c31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/pot_meerca_halloween.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpot_meerca_halloween.gif&h=5af686b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/pot_lutari_pirate.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpot_lutari_pirate.gif&h=1dfd1b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/pot_draik_faerie.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpot_draik_faerie.gif&h=f1d82da7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/transparentpaintbrush.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Ftransparentpaintbrush.gif&h=6e00fb1c&s={SIZE}\" /> </div><br />\n改變寵物顏色的方法，有六種:(1)筆刷、(2)蛻變藥水、(3)變形藥水、(4)實驗室、(5)泉水精靈<br />\n(6)特別方法<br />\n<br />\n例子:<br />\n(1)使用筆刷 <em><span style=\"color: orange;\">(變色不變族)</span></em>:<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色</span>特雷+<span style=\"color: brown;\">殭屍</span>筆刷=<span style=\"color: brown;\">殭屍</span>特雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(2)使用蛻變藥水 <em><span style=\"color: orange;\">(變色及變族)</span></em>:<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">機械</span>狂妄龍+<span style=\"color: green;\">綠色</span>奇俐蛻變藥水=<span style=\"color: green;\">綠色奇俐</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(3)使用變形藥水 <em><span style=\"color: orange;\">(變色及變族)</span></em>:<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">巧克力</span>舒特+朦朦豬<span style=\"color: teal;\">變形</span>藥水=<span style=\"color: teal;\">變形</span>朦朦豬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(4)使用實驗室 <em><span style=\"color: orange;\">(變色或變族，有時加能力)</span></em>:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">集齊9張</span>神秘實驗室地圖先入得 總約值1M&uarr; (100萬以上 目前市價150萬)<br />\n詳情: <a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=labray\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Dlabray&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=f25298ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=labray</a><br />\n(5)泉水精靈 <em><span style=\"color: orange;\">(變色不變族)</span></em>:<br />\n完成泉水精靈索禮後，免費到彩虹池上色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n詳情:<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=fountain\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Dfountain&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=cafdf058\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=fountain</a><br />\n(6)特別方法:<br />\n還有其他為寵物改色的魔力物品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n詳情:<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=alteringitems\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Dalteringitems&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=c80c91de\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=alteringitems</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*<span style=\"color: red;\">神</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">秘</span><span style=\"color: teal;\">色</span><span style=\"color: green;\">彩</span>*</div>&quot;機械、趣蛙琪、MSPP、海綿、果凍、奶油凍、鼻涕、巧克力、黏土、大蒜、冰、熔岩&quot;<br />\n詳情:請自行探究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3368209df61bf992c0e38a0cb0807b76752004","tid":1566131,"uid":21203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:25:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/dubloon10.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fdubloon10.gif&h=926ab35d&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>練寵篇</strong></span></span><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/dubloon10.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fdubloon10.gif&h=926ab35d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>萬劫不復嘅地獄-尼奧競技場</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">尼奧重要既一環 好多時劇情活動需要寵物戰鬥 而且新競技場打贏敵人有獎品 <br />\n以下先介紹寵物訓練</span></div><br />\n- 邊到可以知道我隻寵的能力值？<br />\n競技場裡的寵物狀態: <a href=\"http://www.neopets.com/dome/neopets.phtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neopets.com%2Fdome%2Fneopets.phtml&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=f89ced78\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.neopets.com/dome/neopets.phtml</a><br />\n- 能力值有分邊幾種?<br />\n*<span style=\"color: navy;\">寵物等級</span>: 等級高可以用勁技能<br />\n*<span style=\"color: red;\">力量</span>: 代表在競技場裏的攻擊力加成<br />\n*<span style=\"color: blue;\">防禦</span>: 代表在競技場裏的防禦力加成<br />\n*<span style=\"color: orange;\">速度</span>: 冇鬼用,有件裝要你幾百速度先用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n*<span style=\"color: green;\">耐力</span>: 隻寵的生命值(HP)。<br />\n*<span style=\"color: violet;\">智力</span>: 冇鬼用,有件裝要你成千智力先用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 去邊到訓練先?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">推介1-40Lv. </span> 三條腿船長的海刀劍館<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.neopets.com/pirates/academy.phtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neopets.com%2Fpirates%2Facademy.phtml&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=f5932690\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.neopets.com/pirates/academy.phtml</a><br />\n學費: 達龍幣<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/DMGLLjm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FDMGLLjm.png&h=d2a51376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">特點: 平但慢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">推介40-250Lv.</span> 神秘島武術學校<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.neopets.com/island/training.phtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neopets.com%2Fisland%2Ftraining.phtml&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=f075a173\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.neopets.com/island/training.phtml</a><br />\n學費: 魔符石<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/8ocYvNW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F8ocYvNW.png&h=b14ac945&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://imgur.com/0kMuqwb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F0kMuqwb.png&h=924f98fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">特點: 快但貴</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">250Lv. up</span>神秘忍者訓練學校<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.neopets.com/island/fight_training.phtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neopets.com%2Fisland%2Ffight_training.phtml&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=168a103a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.neopets.com/island/fight_training.phtml</a><br />\n學費: 火山魔符石<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/6jycPjz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F6jycPjz.png&h=b439ee6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">特點: 唔夠等級只會見到道門</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">而提升寵物智力的方法是俾寵物讀書</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>寵物能力加成表</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/YQVjFTt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FYQVjFTt.png&h=46e105ee&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9a246bb08cf11cb8f600f91d55b6cc9e0822cff3","tid":1566131,"uid":21203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:26:29.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/bd_grapesofwrath.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fbd_grapesofwrath.gif&h=006a4432&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>戰鬥篇</strong></span></span><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/bd_grapesofwrath.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fbd_grapesofwrath.gif&h=006a4432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>萬劫不復嘅地獄-尼奧競技場</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">除左練寵之外 打交最緊要係拎武器 以下將介紹尼奧的戰鬥及防禦魔法<br />\n部分裝備極燒錢 高端武器只有富豪先玩得起</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">新手</span>入門裝備<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/bpo_flask_liquidfire.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fbpo_flask_liquidfire.gif&h=b7a71a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://imgur.com/WTnXBvj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FWTnXBvj.png&h=3eab781c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左至右:<br />\nFlask of Liquid Fire(攻8-14icon)、Scroll of Ultranova(攻9.8icon)、Parasol of Unfortunate Demise(防4.4-8icon，光100%防禦)、Magical Healing Potion(回15血/一場一次)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">總計: 5k(5千)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">正常</span>出門裝備<br />\n<img src=\"https://items.jellyneo.net/assets/imgs/items/62038.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitems.jellyneo.net%2Fassets%2Fimgs%2Fitems%2F62038.gif&h=1f3e1207&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/bd_downsize.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fbd_downsize.gif&h=661a9bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://items.jellyneo.net/assets/imgs/items/47475.gif?365\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitems.jellyneo.net%2Fassets%2Fimgs%2Fitems%2F47475.gif%3F365&h=22895339&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://items.jellyneo.net/assets/imgs/items/62844.gif?384\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitems.jellyneo.net%2Fassets%2Fimgs%2Fitems%2F62844.gif%3F384&h=9db8a059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左至右:<br />\nTurned Tooth(攻13-22icon)、Downsize!(全屬性50%防禦/一場一次)、Altadorian Swordbreaker(攻5icon，物理100%防禦)、Cursed Elixir of Neovia(回40血/不會溢補/一場一次)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">總計: 500k(50萬)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">高手</span>破門裝備<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/shw_shuriken.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fshw_shuriken.gif&h=f8489cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/bd_freezeray_random.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fbd_freezeray_random.gif&h=eea9856e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://items.jellyneo.net/assets/imgs/items/65186.gif?205\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitems.jellyneo.net%2Fassets%2Fimgs%2Fitems%2F65186.gif%3F205&h=9dfe8866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左至右:<br />\nShuriken(50%機會凍結對手，50%作出14icon攻擊/凍結後暫時消失/凍結武器限制攜帶一件)、Randomly Firing Freeze Ray(50%機會凍結對手，50%作出4icon攻擊/凍結後暫時消失/凍結武器限制攜帶一件)、Potion of Healing(回90-300血/不會溢補/一場一次/沒有限制攜帶一件)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">總計: 5m(500萬)</span>"},{"pid":"6e2b62eb49a2525b5ae56f13d4dbe1ef40f99ea2","tid":1566131,"uid":40137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:27:04.000Z","msg":"人地咪開左囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[Web][207]尼奧寵物Neopets! 從不知天高與地厚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"71632e845efad0dda8b69c84d44d667319ffd38d","tid":1566131,"uid":21203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">老手</span>爆門裝備<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/bd_sword_lameness.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fbd_sword_lameness.gif&h=eb8b1d44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/darkfaerie_wand.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fdarkfaerie_wand.gif&h=02c470c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/earth_staff.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fearth_staff.gif&h=c91de6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/magic_amuletwater.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fmagic_amuletwater.gif&h=de430504&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/bpo_potion3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fbpo_potion3.gif&h=fa279a32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://items.jellyneo.net/assets/imgs/items/9185.gif?581\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitems.jellyneo.net%2Fassets%2Fimgs%2Fitems%2F9185.gif%3F581&h=a987f214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左至右:<br />\nSword of Lameness(25%作出攻11-20icon，37.5%作出攻12icon，12.5%回100%血，12.5%凍結，12.5%沒有任何效果)、Wand of the Dark Faerie(攻20.9-29icon，光75%反射，血量不足25%時回25%血)、<br />\nIllusens Staff(攻13.6-16icon，暗100%防禦，有條件下光75%反射，血量不足20%時回20%血)、Thyoras Tear(全屬性100%防禦/一場一次)、Leaded Elemental Vial(回100%血/一場一次)、Freezing Potion(100%凍結/凍結後暫時消失/凍結武器限制攜帶一件)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">總計: 165m(1億6500萬)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">神手</span>無價裝備<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/bd_superpea.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fbd_superpea.gif&h=ec1bb984&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/bd_faerieacornslingshot.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fbd_faerieacornslingshot.gif&h=d181bfa3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/rod_darknova.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Frod_darknova.gif&h=7b05b3d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/bd_moehog_skull.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fbd_moehog_skull.gif&h=6a766cb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左至右:<br />\nSuper Attack Pea(攻32icon)、Faerie Slingshot(攻4.3-62icon)、<br />\nRod of Dark Nova(攻4icon，火&amp;暗100%防禦，回6-60血，產生3個黑暗新星)、<br />\nMoehog Skull(攻15icon，防10icon，100%凍結/一場一次)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">總計: 一粒豆已經一億，話左窮人玩唔起架啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">外掛級</span>裝備<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/PCGFOvU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FPCGFOvU.png&h=4219b69b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左至右:<br />\nDarigan Shield Of Malevolence(攻30icon，全屬性100%防禦/多次使用)、<br />\nDarigans Orb(攻25icon，100%凍結/多次使用)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">總計:GM都未必有</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">*P.S.以上裝備資料由&quot;慢魔麼三世&quot;獨家整理,有血有汗, 私自轉載者死全家*</span>"},{"pid":"fcd2f962be703f4c45b99efe428df4914171cf98","tid":1566131,"uid":21203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:27:59.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">延伸閱讀</div></strong></ins><br />\n英文攻略網站:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sunnyneo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sunnyneo.com%2F&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=b0610fa5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sunnyneo.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=6df7dc61\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/</a><br />\n價格查詢網站:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.neocodex.us/forum/itemdb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neocodex.us%2Fforum%2Fitemdb%2F&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=58ab3dc4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.neocodex.us/forum/itemdb/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://items.jellyneo.net/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fitems.jellyneo.net%2Findex.php&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=00b5c274\" target=\"_blank\">http://items.jellyneo.net/index.php</a><br />\n競技場詳細攻略網站:<br />\n<a href=\"http://battlepedia.jellyneo.net/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbattlepedia.jellyneo.net%2Findex.php&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=e1e5f10f\" target=\"_blank\">http://battlepedia.jellyneo.net/index.php</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://battlepedia.thedailyneopets.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbattlepedia.thedailyneopets.com%2F&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=0a5ad455\" target=\"_blank\">http://battlepedia.thedailyneopets.com/</a><br />\n尼奧寵物討論區縮寫大全:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/dictionary/?show=all\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2Fdictionary%2F%3Fshow%3Dall&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=075fca59\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/dictionary/?show=all</a><br />\n尼奧寵物孤兒網<br />\n<a href=\"http://lost.quiggle.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flost.quiggle.org%2F&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=d5e71a86\" target=\"_blank\">http://lost.quiggle.org/</a>"},{"pid":"ab21147638ae34c693190476cfbaf7ca03d97e7e","tid":1566131,"uid":21203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:28:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 補充區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></div><br />\n*補充一下, 咩叫競技場icon*<br />\nicon係競技場最基本既攻守設定<br />\n分攻同防<br />\n重得荒謬的戰錘 可以打出 3草 3空氣 3物理 的icon<br />\n如果對手有防具 例如樹葉盾，防 5草 5水 3物理 icon<br />\n咁你打人就得返 3空氣 icon<br />\n再跟返個表睇你幾多力量 再乘返 就係實際傷害(建基於雙方的攻擊和防禦是在同一個階級)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GS2nY3t.png?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGS2nY3t.png%3F1&h=afef7d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就好似咁 場戰鬥有攻擊 防禦 回血<br />\n總之icon愈多愈勁 不過亦有例外 因為有d icon比較難防 例如火<br />\n&ldquo;neomail 講中文會亂碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個問題咁多年都無解決 要轉日文見睇到&rdquo;<br />\nBy: 獨領生活<br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">*<span style=\"color: brown;\">被遺忘的海灘</span>*</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.neopets.com/games/treasure.phtml?type=shore\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neopets.com%2Fgames%2Ftreasure.phtml%3Ftype%3Dshore&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=bb76e257\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.neopets.com/games/treasure.phtml?type=shore</a><br />\n集齊9張&quot;<span style=\"color: maroon;\">被遺忘的海灘藏寶圖片段</span>&quot;先入得<br />\n好平 新手容易中 <span style=\"color: blue;\">海盜特雷蛋</span> or <span style=\"color: red;\">魔力海盜狂妄龍絨毛玩具</span><br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\n物品易脫手= ETS = Easy To Sell<br />\n物品難脫手= HTS = Hard To Sell<br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\nAmnesia獨家製作 雪球整理<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.neopets.com/~Krinkle88444\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neopets.com%2F~Krinkle88444&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=58287926\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.neopets.com/~Krinkle88444</a><br />\nNeoQuest I &amp; 絨毛玩具大亨攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1QGnNor-7GIhBD69_qGU4N1eIJaCRXWqMFYFs9sXc8pE/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1QGnNor-7GIhBD69_qGU4N1eIJaCRXWqMFYFs9sXc8pE%2Fedit&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=d825da76\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1QGnNor-7GIhBD69_qGU4N1eIJaCRXWqMFYFs9sXc8pE/edit</a><br />\nBy: 李起光<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*以上所有攻略由&quot;慢魔麼三世&quot;巴打整合制作,特別嗚謝眾巴絲協助。*<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">*所有攻略不得私自轉載及投稿尼奧時報*</span><br />\n*最後更新:16-3-2019*</div>"},{"pid":"91b0e92fd4d16075aaffd7b7636c9b102fc686db","tid":1566131,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:29:43.000Z","msg":"開咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88223219a3f1396f52dee998dfdbc83c60ac707c","tid":1566131,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:31:45.000Z","msg":"[Web][207]尼奧寵物Neopets! 從不知天高與地厚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566045</a><br />\n<br />\n重覆開post都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9981f54fde2068fe2de4adc95a71c670b3e5f22","tid":1566131,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:22:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pi